                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add striped dir feature flag to lustre_mdt_attrs::lma_incompat, so when MDT is downgraded, striped dir will not be able to be accessed by old MDT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
